data.title: Thunder 106
data.text:
Win ‘Em Before You Can Buy ‘Em: Warren Zeiders at the Stone Pony Summer Stage in Asbury Park – May 2nd!

Listen to The Afternoon Ride w/ Chris VanZant for your chance to win a pair of tickets before you can buy them! For more info visit LiveNation.com!

Read More

Kenny Chesney Ticket Blitz at Freehold Ford

Join Thunder 106 at Freehold Ford on Thursday, August 15th from 6 PM to 8 PM for a Kenny Chesney Ticket Blitz! We’ll be giving away multiple pairs of Thunder Party Suite tickets to see the Kenny Chesney and Zac Brown Band “Sun Goes Down Tour” at MetLife Stadium in East Rutherford on August 17th! One grand prize winner will receive a pair of floor seats! You have to be there to win so be sure to come to snag these tickets and check out all of the incredible deals Freehold Ford has to offer!

Read More

Ride and Slide Passes to Casino Pier and Breakwater Beach in Seaside Heights!

Listen to The Afternoon Ride w/ Chris VanZant for your chance to win a 4-pack of tickets!! For more info visit CasinoPierNJ.com!

Read More

Thunder 106 presents Kameron Marlowe at the Starland Ballroom in Sayreville – October 11th!

Listen to Pork Roll and Eggs with Nina and Tom weekday mornings for your chance to win a pair of tickets! For more info visit AXS.com!

Six Flags Great Adventure in Jackson 50th Anniversary!

Listen to Pork Roll and Eggs with Nina and Tom weekday mornings for your chance to win a pair of tickets! One Grand prize winner will also receive a meal and parking! For more info visit SixFlags.com/GreatAdventure!

Jelly Roll Ticket Blitz at the Freehold Raceway Mall on August 24th

Join Thunder 106 at the Freehold Raceway Mall (3710 Route 9) on Saturday, August 24th from Noon-2pm for a Jelly Roll Ticket Blitz! We’ll be giving away multiple pairs of Thunder Party Suite tickets to see Jelly Roll at the Prudential Center in Newark on September 29th! You have to be there to win so be sure to come to snag these tickets and check out the Freehold Raceway Mall’s wide variety of popular shops and delicious dining options!

Kenny Chesney Sun Goes Down 2024 Tour Contest sponsored by John Guire Supply

Enter for your chance to win a pair of tickets to see the Kenny Chesney Sun Goes Down 2024 Tour with Zac Brown Band and special guests Megan Moroney and Uncle Kracker at MetLife Stadium on Saturday, August 17th! Contest sponsored by John Guire Supply.

Read More

Summertime Tastes Like Miller Lite Contest

Share with us your favorite grilling recipes and food you love to pair with Miller Lite, for a chance to “Get Your Next Round on Miller Lite”, a $40 Gift Card you can spend on whatever summer pleasure you like, like a round of ice cold Miller Lite! Listen to TJ every weeknight at 7:20pm to hear him share his favorite recipes. Plus, you will also be entered to win a custom Miller Lite Gas Grill and in the running for a chance at the Grand Prize, a Flyaway to see Garth Brooks in Las Vegas!

Read More

Coors Light VIP Music Experience Contest

Enter for your chance to win the Coors Light VIP Music Experience, which includes: Coors Light Speaker Cooler, a Pair of Coors Light Backpack Chairs and a Getaway with 2 day pass to see Lainey Wilson in Ocean City Maryland, with hotel stay and a $200 gift card! Plus, don't forget to listen to Nina and Tom from the Pork Roll & Eggs Morning Show every weekday to tell them what shows you're looking forward to this summer. Then, every Friday they will pick one winner to send to one of Coors Light's Chill Music Experiences, tickets to summer shows...

Live Green, Save Green Guide & Contest

Conserving energy not only helps the planet, but could help your wallet! You can download the Live Green Save Green Booklet and enter for a chance to win an Ecobee Smart Thermostat from New Jersey Natural Gas, designed to lower energy costs and maximize comfort or a Rachio Water Sprinkler 8-Zone Smart Meter from New Jersey American Water!
